	(48,1,'2014-05-19 15:21:31','2014-05-19 15:21:31','<div class=\"col-md-12\">\r\n	<h2>Do you want to sell your apartment?</h2>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"col-md-6\">\r\nHow would you like to see your apartment advertised on the DSS website? We are trained sales agents that are complemented by experienced managers. We can sell your apartment at the highest price in short period of time. Our relationships with NYC’s largest lenders provide buyers with immediate pre- approvals and letters that show transaction. A group of real estate attorneys, who specialize in Manhattan co-ops and condo markets, support our buyers and sellers in completing a transaction. We will handle all aspects when it comes to the selling your property.</div>\r\n<div class=\"col-md-6\">\r\nAn agent will be assigned to you and they will interact with you throughout the sales process to ensure and facilitate a price and a timely closing. As a small firm, we produce large results. We customize our marketing skills to benefit your needs. We are here to help you in any way we can. This will help you to quickly expose your apartment to thousands of buyers. Why wait? Call us now!</div>','Sales','','publish','open','open','','sales','','','2014-05-27 18:42:24','2014-05-27 18:42:24','',0,'http://localhost:8888/dssserv/?page_id=48',0,'page','',0),
