	(105,1,'2014-05-27 18:34:01','2014-05-27 18:34:01','<div class=\"col-md-6\">\r\n\r\nDSS Services LLC has a complete line of insurance products for those seeking the ultimate insurance in customer satisfaction and professionalism. We offer extensive amounts of coverage for Life, Health, Auto, Home, and Commercial/Business. Our extraordinarily wide range of business goes from a single person to a company with revenues in the millions. No task is too big or too small!\r\n\r\nDSS Services LLC makes meeting your insurance needs an experience you will never forget! Due to the seriousness of getting insurance in today\'s society, we will work with you and depict every single last detail to customize your insurance needs for the maximum amount of coverage with the minimal costs.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"col-md-6\">\r\n\r\nDSS Services LLC also offers defensive driving courses to help save 10% on your auto insurance premiums or reduce points off of your license. Space is limited so call today to reserve your space.\r\n\r\nDSS Services LLC works with an extensive amount of insurance companies to provide the necessary coverage for all of your insurance needs. Please contact us today for your free quote!\r\n\r\n<div class=\"row\">\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Apartment Building</li>\r\n	<li>Mold and Fungus</li>\r\n	<li>Lead Coverage</li>\r\n	<li>Auto Personal</li>\r\n	<li>Home Renters, Condos and Apartments</li>\r\n	<li>Fire</li>\r\n	<li>All types of insurance</li>\r\n	<li> Commercial Business</li>\r\n	<li>Professional Liability</li>\r\n	<li>Life</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>','Insurance','','inherit','open','open','','52-revision-v1','','','2014-05-27 18:34:01','2014-05-27 18:34:01','',52,'http://localhost:8888/dssserv/52-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),
	(106,1,'2014-05-27 18:35:24','2014-05-27 18:35:24','<div class=\"col-md-6\">\r\n	<p>What every landlord should know is how to handle tenant deposits. If you are managing a property, you are keeping track of the tenants that belong to your property. The issue is security deposits, and how they play a part of your property losses. Managing a property means collecting rent from tenants, making sure the terms and conditions laid out in the lease agreement are in compliance, and that are clearly stated.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"col-md-6\">\r\n	<p>A property needs to be clean and well organize for the tenants. If there are apartments that are empty then they need to be quickly filled in so you can gain finances out of it. The goal is to keep the units full and at the highest rent per square foot possible. A property has to have good curb appeal, structure, landscaping, common areas and parking in clean condition. Make sure that tenants comply with rental policies and procedures are also important. Supervise repairs and maintenance work, conduct inspections from time to time and maintain an organized system of collecting rental payments and security deposit.</p>\r\n</div>','Property Management','','inherit','open','open','','54-revision-v1','','','2014-05-27 18:35:24','2014-05-27 18:35:24','',54,'http://localhost:8888/dssserv/54-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),
	(107,1,'2014-05-27 18:39:03','2014-05-27 18:39:03','<h2>Do you want to rent your apartment?</h2>\r\n<div class=\"col-md-6\">\r\nA good way to put your apartment up for rent is by advertising it in an ad or newspaper. A virtual tour of the apartment can provide a better visual and generate more prospective clients. This can enhance the marketing of the property. By taking pictures of selected areas of the apartment, it can also be a photo layout of the property. The apartment listing will be immediately available to the entire brokerage community, including all of Manhattan’s real estate board of New York and their cooperating brokers and their renters.\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"col-md-6\">\r\nWhen it comes down to renting an apartment, time management is important. Apartments have to get rented as soon as possible. DSS Services LLC has a list of pre qualified renters. Agents are committed to getting the job done to the highest level of personal customer service. We provide customers with up to date comparables of currently available properties. We are highly experienced in renting apartments. An agent will interact with you to negotiate a price and to figure out a timely approval to secure the occupancy of your apartment. Why wait, Call us now!\r\n</div>','Rentals','','inherit','open','open','','46-revision-v1','','','2014-05-27 18:39:03','2014-05-27 18:39:03','',46,'http://localhost:8888/dssserv/46-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),
	(108,1,'2014-05-27 18:40:04','2014-05-27 18:40:04','<div class=\"row\">\n	<h2>Do you want to rent your apartment?</h2>\n</div>\n<div class=\"col-md-6\">\nA good way to put your apartment up for rent is by advertising it in an ad or newspaper. A virtual tour of the apartment can provide a better visual and generate more prospective clients. This can enhance the marketing of the property. By taking pictures of selected areas of the apartment, it can also be a photo layout of the property. The apartment listing will be immediately available to the entire brokerage community, including all of Manhattan’s real estate board of New York and their cooperating brokers and their renters.\n</div>\n<div class=\"col-md-6\">\nWhen it comes down to renting an apartment, time management is important. Apartments have to get rented as soon as possible. DSS Services LLC has a list of pre qualified renters. Agents are committed to getting the job done to the highest level of personal customer service. We provide customers with up to date comparables of currently available properties. We are highly experienced in renting apartments. An agent will interact with you to negotiate a price and to figure out a timely approval to secure the occupancy of your apartment. Why wait, Call us now!\n</div>','Rentals','','inherit','open','open','','46-autosave-v1','','','2014-05-27 18:40:04','2014-05-27 18:40:04','',46,'http://localhost:8888/dssserv/46-autosave-v1/',0,'revision','',0),
	(109,1,'2014-05-27 18:40:06','2014-05-27 18:40:06','<div class=\"row\">\r\n	<h2>Do you want to rent your apartment?</h2>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"col-md-6\">\r\nA good way to put your apartment up for rent is by advertising it in an ad or newspaper. A virtual tour of the apartment can provide a better visual and generate more prospective clients. This can enhance the marketing of the property. By taking pictures of selected areas of the apartment, it can also be a photo layout of the property. The apartment listing will be immediately available to the entire brokerage community, including all of Manhattan’s real estate board of New York and their cooperating brokers and their renters.\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"col-md-6\">\r\nWhen it comes down to renting an apartment, time management is important. Apartments have to get rented as soon as possible. DSS Services LLC has a list of pre qualified renters. Agents are committed to getting the job done to the highest level of personal customer service. We provide customers with up to date comparables of currently available properties. We are highly experienced in renting apartments. An agent will interact with you to negotiate a price and to figure out a timely approval to secure the occupancy of your apartment. Why wait, Call us now!\r\n</div>','Rentals','','inherit','open','open','','46-revision-v1','','','2014-05-27 18:40:06','2014-05-27 18:40:06','',46,'http://localhost:8888/dssserv/46-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),
	(110,1,'2014-05-27 18:40:35','2014-05-27 18:40:35','<div class=\"col-md-12\">\r\n	<h2>Do you want to rent your apartment?</h2>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"col-md-6\">\r\nA good way to put your apartment up for rent is by advertising it in an ad or newspaper. A virtual tour of the apartment can provide a better visual and generate more prospective clients. This can enhance the marketing of the property. By taking pictures of selected areas of the apartment, it can also be a photo layout of the property. The apartment listing will be immediately available to the entire brokerage community, including all of Manhattan’s real estate board of New York and their cooperating brokers and their renters.\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"col-md-6\">\r\nWhen it comes down to renting an apartment, time management is important. Apartments have to get rented as soon as possible. DSS Services LLC has a list of pre qualified renters. Agents are committed to getting the job done to the highest level of personal customer service. We provide customers with up to date comparables of currently available properties. We are highly experienced in renting apartments. An agent will interact with you to negotiate a price and to figure out a timely approval to secure the occupancy of your apartment. Why wait, Call us now!\r\n</div>','Rentals','','inherit','open','open','','46-revision-v1','','','2014-05-27 18:40:35','2014-05-27 18:40:35','',46,'http://localhost:8888/dssserv/46-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),
	(111,1,'2014-05-27 18:42:24','2014-05-27 18:42:24','<div class=\"col-md-12\">\r\n	<h2>Do you want to sell your apartment?</h2>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"col-md-6\">\r\nHow would you like to see your apartment advertised on the DSS website? We are trained sales agents that are complemented by experienced managers. We can sell your apartment at the highest price in short period of time. Our relationships with NYC’s largest lenders provide buyers with immediate pre- approvals and letters that show transaction. A group of real estate attorneys, who specialize in Manhattan co-ops and condo markets, support our buyers and sellers in completing a transaction. We will handle all aspects when it comes to the selling your property.</div>\r\n<div class=\"col-md-6\">\r\nAn agent will be assigned to you and they will interact with you throughout the sales process to ensure and facilitate a price and a timely closing. As a small firm, we produce large results. We customize our marketing skills to benefit your needs. We are here to help you in any way we can. This will help you to quickly expose your apartment to thousands of buyers. Why wait? Call us now!</div>','Sales','','inherit','open','open','','48-revision-v1','','','2014-05-27 18:42:24','2014-05-27 18:42:24','',48,'http://localhost:8888/dssserv/48-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0);
